13
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,260
Qian, Kan, Gen, Zhen,

14
00:01:48,379 --> 00:01:49,459
Xun, Li, Kun, Dui.

15
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,180
Dunjia,

16
00:01:50,379 --> 00:01:50,799
Open!

17
00:02:05,459 --> 00:02:06,060
Hubby.

18
00:02:09,139 --> 00:02:10,219
Why are you hiding in my room?

19
