I'm just teasing you.

27
00:02:41,879 --> 00:02:43,139
I'm wearing something underneath.

28
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,599
Scaredy-cat.

29
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,639
I have to say,

30
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:49,259
Wu Ming,

31
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,759
