You...

47
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:57,599
Are you all right?

48
00:03:58,919 --> 00:04:00,639
Do I look all right to you?

49
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:03,000
I just wanted to warm your bed,

50
00:04:03,099 --> 00:04:04,919
