237
00:12:44,299 --> 00:12:46,299
I can treat any and all men's health issues.

238
00:12:46,919 --> 00:12:47,600
Ming Ming,

239
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,679
how about I give you

240
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:51,639
